responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "38B9B16543E2EF90EAF27A938947EEA5", "Engraved on the shield of an ancient plague doctor. Ingenious! I must get on this at once. If this formula hold true, then together we might just save the resettlement of this realm. I am in your debt. Kyron Keep You. ")
